org.apache.ambari.server.serveraction.kerberos.stageutils

Class ResolvedKerberosKeytab

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.serveraction.kerberos.stageutils.ResolvedKerberosKeytab

  • public class ResolvedKerberosKeytab
extends Object
    Class that represents keytab. Contains principals that mapped to host. Same keytab can have different set of principals on different hosts for different services. Each principal identified by host and keytab it belongs to and contain mapping that shows in which services and components given principal used.
